query:
query SearchArticles($apiVersion: String, $artist: String, $category: String, $geotag: String, $limit: Int!, $endDate: String, $startDate: String, $visibility: String!, $phrase: String, $field: String, $paginationToken: String, $published: Boolean) {
  searchArticles(
    apiVersion: $apiVersion
    artist: $artist
    category: $category
    geotag: $geotag
    limit: $limit
    endDate: $endDate
    startDate: $startDate
    visibility: $visibility
    phrase: $phrase
    field: $field
    paginationToken: $paginationToken
    published: $published
  ) {
    articles {
      ...Article_v1
      __typename
    }
    paginationToken
    __typename
  }
}

fragment Article_v1 on Article {
  id
  artists
  attribution
  categories
  contentLang
  description
  domain
  favicon
  geotag
  imageUrl
  published
  publishDate
  tags
  title
  url
  visibility
  dateCreated
  dateUpdated
  __typename
}
